            "text": "I can tell you're in a panic storm right now. Let's ground ourselves before we do anything else.\n\n**Look around the room and find:**\n≡ƒæÇ **5** things you can see\nΓ£ï **4** things you can touch\n≡ƒæé **3** things you can hear\n≡ƒæâ **2** things you can smell\n≡ƒæà **1** thing you can taste\n\nTake a deep breath. Are you back with me?",
