            "text": "Let's lower your heart rate together. Follow my count:\n\n1. **Inhale** for 4 seconds...\n2. **Hold** for 4 seconds...\n3. **Exhale** for 4 seconds...\n4. **Hold** for 4 seconds...\n\nDo this two more times. I'm right here.",
